    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"flicker\" is just more suffering. if you look at it through a lens of efficiency or even just minimizing pain, why is it \"better\" to keep struggling through the chaos just to experience it? isn't it more logical to just accept the zero-sum nature of everything and stop the struggle now?",
